high_descs: Move forward to the counter.

Turn around, move forward, turn to the right, move forward, turn to the right.
Put the bar of soap on the second shelf to the right of the gray bottle.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the left and go to the bathtub.
Pick up the pink bar of soap in the bathtub.
Turn around, go to the toilet, hang a right, go forward, hang a right and go to the counter.
Put the bar of soap to the right of the bar of soap on the second shelf.

high_descs: Walk to the counter ahead of you.
Pick up the bar of soap in between the two white rags.
Move further away from the counter to face the shelves below the counter.
Place the soap on the shelf.
Turn right, walk to the tub on the left.
Pick up the bar of soap to the left of the rag.
Walk back to the counter on the right side.
Place the second bar of soap to the right of the first bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: To move two bars of soap to the shelf.
